name: Celebrity Big Brother
overview: Follow a group of American celebrities living together in a house outfitted with 87 HD cameras and more than 100 microphones, recording their every move 24 hours a day. Each week, someone will be voted out of the house, with the last remaining Houseguest receiving a grand prize.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Eleven celebrities from all walks of life including an NBA champion, a UFC legend, a Tony Award-winning actress, a chart-topping musician, a model, a television personality and a TV host, among others enter the house to compete for the $250,000 grand prize.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: The Houseguests learn more about the game changing gift bag twist. Will the recast power dethrone Shannon? With nominations looming, which celebrities will be targeted?

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Who will win the Power of Veto and will it be used to save either Chuck or James from eviction? Plus, who will be the first celebrity evicted from the house?

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: There are still 10 celebrities left in the game, find out who among them will rise to power in the next Head of Household competition and which two houseguests will be nominated for eviction.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Who will win the Power of Veto and will it be used to save either Keshia or Omarosa from eviction? Plus, who will be the next celebrity evicted from the house?

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Find out which celebrity rises to power and which ones end up on the chopping block.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Who will win the Power of Veto and will it be used to save either James or Shannon from eviction? Plus, who will be the next celebrity evicted from the house?

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Only eight celebrities are left in the game, who among them will rise to power as the next head of household? Also two houseguests are nominated for eviction.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Which veto did America choose to shake up the game and will it be used to save either Ross or Brandi from eviction? Plus, who will be the next celebrity evicted from the house?

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: There are now seven celebrities left in the game, find out who will become the new Head of Household and which two houseguests will be nominated for eviction.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Who will win the Power of Veto and will it be used to save either Ariana or Brandi from eviction? Plus it's Double Eviction Night where two houseguests will be evicted.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Omarosa reveals more about her time working in the White House. Plus, the Head of Household competition gets underway.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: Who will become the next Head of Household and secure a spot in the Final Four? Plus, with three competitions and two evictions left, who will defy the odds and emerge as the first ever winner of Celebrity Big Brother?

episodes.name: Episode 1

episodes.name: Episode 3

episodes.name: Episode 4

episodes.name: Episode 5

episodes.name: Episode 6

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Who will receive the Power of the Publicist? Plus, who will rise to power as the news HoH, and who will be nominated for eviction?

episodes.name: Season 2, Episode 8
episodes.overview: Who will win the power of veto? And will it save Candy or Joey from the chopping block? Plus, who will be the next celebrity evicted from the house?

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: A jam packed hour where a new Head of Household will be crowned, the Power of Veto will be played out, and another celebrity will be sent out the front door.

episodes.name: Episode 10

episodes.name: Episode 11

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: CELEBRITY BIG BROTHER follows a group of celebrities living together in a house outfitted with over 90 HD cameras and over 100 microphones, recording their every move 24 hours a day, and having no contact with the outside world. Each week, one or more celebrity Houseguests will be voted out of the house, with the last remaining Houseguest receiving the grand prize of $250,000.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Tonight, the Houseguests find out whats in the Gala Gift and how it promises to shake up the game. Plus, Meisha is a master of take downs but who will she put up for eviction?

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Who will win the Power of Veto? And will it be used to save either Carson or Mirai from the block? Plus, it's the first live eviction! Which celeb will be sent packing? And will the Gala Gift send someone not on the block out the door?

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Tonight, a new HOH will be crowned and two new celebrities will be targeted for eviction.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: It's been a wild few days in the Big Brother house, and it's not over yet. Tonight a veto will be won, and a new celebrity will be walking out the door.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Tonight, a new head of household will be crowned. A past celebrity houseguest makes a surprise return. And two more celebs will find themselves on the chopping block.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Who will win the Power of Veto, and will it be used to save either Cynthia or Carson from eviction? Plus, who will be the next celebrity sent packing?

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Who will go from powder to power, and which two Houseguests will hit the block. Plus, it's the Sunday night super showdown you've been waiting for.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Will the Veto seal Shanna's fate, or could Miesha or Todd be walking out the door? Either way, another celebrity will be Evicted!

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: We are down to the Sensational Six. Who will rise to power with only one week left in the game? And which two houseguests will hit the block?

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Tonight, a make or break power of veto will be played. Will it save one of the nominees? Plus, Hollywood star and BB super-fan Jerry O'Connell gives insights on the season.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Tonight it's all new episode filled with never before seen moments from this season. Witness the laughs, strategy, and drama you didn't see as the final five make their way to the finale.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: Tonight, with the final five only having four days of gameplay left, the head of household competition is more important than ever. Which celebrity will rise to power? Plus, it's the most over-the-top nomination ceremony in the history of the game. Who will end up on the block?

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: Will the power of veto save Lamar or Todd from the block? Plus, not one, but two celebrities will be booted, because its double eviction night baby!This is the last stop before finale, who will be left standing after this crazy night?

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: The winner and America's favorite celebrity houseguest is revealed on the season finale of Celebrity Big Brother.
